{"tid":2300061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林作爆老母是「跳舞群組」 已走佬上大陸","createTime":"2020-11-25T08:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T09:08:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7758d2632f63e822f6cddcd38b916cc2a82bcae8","tid":2300061,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2810000/2811951/LAM20201114_64364564576345_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2810000%2F2811951%2FLAM20201114_64364564576345_1024_600.jpg&h=c12387e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林作在社交平台常發布惹火言論，而林作跟母親的關係更常成新聞焦點。今日林作突然在社交平台發文，聲稱林母是「跳舞群組」，而現已返內地，疑似踢爆母親行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n林作在facebook發文，寫道：「我媽媽係跳舞群組嘅。不過佢醒目，收到風有人有嘢，走咗佬先。老母永遠係至醒目。依家喺內地風流快活。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2810000/2811951/lam_123_20201125_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2810000%2F2811951%2Flam_123_20201125_600.jpg&h=6be4d08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（FB圖片）<br />\n<br />\n林作未有對事件多加解釋，亦未知所說是否屬實還是講笑，但網民就紛紛留言，指林作表面讚母親醒目，實則踢爆媽媽行蹤，又有網民擔心林母會把病毒傳入內地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2810000/2811951/LAM20201114_0008_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2810000%2F2811951%2FLAM20201114_0008_1024_600.jpg&h=0675e0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經常在社交平台言行出位的林作，早前已在社交平台發長文，力陳媽媽王莉妮種種不是，當中包括直指她對裕美不尊重，聲明拒絕與林母再有任何商業合作。<br />\n<br />\n林母因公開不滿兒子跟裕美拍拖，常數落林作女友種種不是，因而令林作跟母親常就女友問題而起爭端。<br />\n<br />\n林作明言：「我無法接受媽媽對權貴的奉承、對平凡人的不屑。我無法接受媽媽的拜金、價值觀的庸俗。」更指媽媽一直對女友裕美不尊重，明言母親「食古不化」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://topick.hket .com/article/2811951</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ada6d3e7021cd166d789fc89ca0f7fb0e05f303e","tid":2300061,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9107716f045187fc18c9a4d7865e7de28ce6f91e","tid":2300061,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08f9e427b69f342f75fbb03f5ec8ed1f2310fda","tid":2300061,"uid":8478,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c928e3f04c8f2e0579873b68add181f0baec979","tid":2300061,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"他有很多跳舞爸爸"},{"pid":"7e0d5c58c81ab2c7d4aede644669833e457a721c","tid":2300061,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"呢d真係識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4945cee99aa58add3fbc7d7c10685ba9d6b3e421","tid":2300061,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣讀書讀到傻撚左，十A女友唔愛，搞隻傻閫，而家仲搞鳩自己老母，好擔心佢老母返大陸俾撚哂副身家俾D鴨店"},{"pid":"9f2eb9652eabc4906e9ced6ea49b29672853efda","tid":2300061,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:41:51.000Z","msg":"老母夠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{